net.finmath.time

Class Tenor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.finmath.time.TimeDiscretization
      • net.finmath.time.Tenor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Double>, TenorInterface, TimeDiscretizationInterface

    public class Tenor
extends TimeDiscretization
implements TenorInterface
    Implements a time discretization based on dates using a reference date and an daycount convention / year fraction. The time as a double is represented as the year fraction from the reference date.
    Author:
    Christian Fries
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
